Package org.apache.jena.jdbc.metadata

Class MetadataSchema

java.lang.Object
org.apache.jena.jdbc.metadata.MetadataSchema
public class MetadataSchema extends Object
Helper class containing constants pertaining to the columns returned by various methods of a DatabaseMetaData implementation
